comments: George (LAC) swipes his arm up and makes contact with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
George (LAC) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position as he contests Muscala's (OKC) shot near the rim.
The ball makes contact with the baseline, and Mann (LAC) is the last player to touch the ball.  Possession should have been awarded to Oklahoma City.
Giddy (OKC) cleanly deflects the ball away from George (LAC) during his drive.
Jackson (LAC) is moving alongside Giddey's (OKC) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.

Replay review of the foul called on Mann (LAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Mann (LAC) does not maintain verticality and makes contact with Bazley's (OKC) arm as he is starting his upward shooting motion.
George (LAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Bazley (OKC).

Jackson (LAC) receives the ball and does not gain full control of the ball.  Upon gaining control, he establishes his right foot as his pivot foot and slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Williams (OKC) is moving alongside Jackson's (LAC) path and legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) cleanly deflects the ball away from George (LAC).
Bazley (OKC) kicks the ball away from Mann (LAC) as they attempt to secure the loose ball.
Williams (OKC) commits a take foul on Kennard (LAC).
George (LAC) is moving alongside Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and cleanly dislodges the ball from Gilgeous-Alexander at the end of his drive.
George (LAC) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Oklahoma City.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) overtly and abruptly kicks his leg out and avoids making contact with Mann (LAC) during his jump shot.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) commits a take foul on Jackson (LAC).
